original_title: Patayan Files: Ang Pinakamalalaking Murder Cases Ng Dekada '90
overview: Vizconde Massacre -the trial of the century, Flor Contemplacion's story, the case that outraged Filipinos, and more horrifying deaths. Cheche Lazaro's Probe Archives goes in-depth on the controversy behind the gruesome crimes that shocked the entire country during the 90s.
title: Patayan Files: Ang Pinakamalalaking Murder Cases Ng Dekada '90
